# Terraform - {{REPO_INFRA_NAME}}

## Formatting

- Indentation: {{INFRA_INDENT_SPACES}} spaces
- Max line length: {{INFRA_MAX_LINE_LENGTH}} characters (aligned with .editorconfig)
- `terraform fmt -recursive` is applied via pre-commit

## Module structure

- Each layer has: `main.tf`, `variables.tf`, `provider.tf`, `datasources.tf`, `backend.tf` (if state)
- Variables in UPPER_SNAKE_CASE
- Use `data` for existing resources, `resource` for new ones

## Provider

- Azure: `azurerm` and `azapi` with `use_oidc = true`
- Backend: `azurerm` with `use_oidc = true` and `use_azuread_auth = true`

## Modules

- Source: `../../modules/<module-name>`
- Available modules: `ias-subnet`, `mssql`, `subnet`

## Provider versions

Defined in `versions.tf` of each layer (required_providers).
Do not duplicate in rules — always modify versions.tf to change azurerm, azapi, random, etc.
